                                        <p>
                        <hi rend="background(yellow)">Hastes plongeantes visibles sur le haut de
                            l’acte.</hi>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324640" xml:id="d1e131750" corresp="Hugues de Noyers, évêque d'Auxerre (1183-1206)">Hugo, Dei gratia <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#290942" xml:id="d1e131752" corresp="Auxerre (diocèse) ( - 1790)">Autissiodorensis</orgName>
                            episcopus</persName>, omnibus ad quos litere presentes pervenerint, in
                        Domino salutem. Notum fieri volumus quod <persName key="d1e11899" xml:id="d1e131756">Ebrardus <addName>
                                <foreign>Rebos</foreign>
                            </addName>
                        </persName> et uxor ejus <lb n="2" />
                        <space /> et filii eorum <persName key="d1e11905" xml:id="d1e131765">Stephanus</persName> et <persName key="d1e11911" xml:id="d1e131768">Landricus</persName> in presentia nostra vendiderunt monachis de
                            <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e131772" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">
                            <sic>Fontenoio</sic>
                        </orgName> vineam quam habebant in <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324968" xml:id="d1e131776" corresp="Nantala">Nantala</placeName>. <lb n="3" /> pro <num>c</num> et
                            <num>xxv</num> libris provin[ensis] monete. Nos autem prefatis
                        concessimus monachis quod si aliquis illam venditionem impedire voluerit,
                        qui nostre <lb n="4" /> sit subditus potestati aut ipsum a sua faciemus
                        cessare calumpnia, aut de ipso in quantum jus dictaverit ad petitionem
                        predictorum mo<lb n="5" break="no" />nachorum justitiam faciemus. In hujus
                        rei testimonium, presens scriptum nostro munivimus sigillo. Datum anno
                        incarnationis dominice <num>m°<lb n="6" /> c° <space />lxxx <space />
                        vi°</num>.</p>
                
